title: OBSESSION ALERT!! The HP "SPROCKET" Mini Photo Printer (Planners and Scrapbooking)
description:
I purchased this printer a few months ago and I can't say enough about it. It is super easy to use, pretty, and creates great photos with fun designs. Check out the video to see a demo of my latest obsession! Below is a list of the items featured in the video, just click on the item to be directed to where you can  get one for yourself!! Also, click the "Subscribe" button on my channel to get all the latest videos from One Joyous Skip (Mamie Carson).

My YouTube Channel: www.youtube.com/c/mamiecarson

Blog: www.onejoyousskip.com

Facebook: www.facebook.com/onejoyousskip

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Sn_Ez

Instagram: https://instagram.com/onejoyousskip

Etsy:https://www.etsy.com/shop/OneJoyousSkip

My Pinterest Board:  https://www.pinterest.com/mommywadz/one-joyous-skip/
